      <div type="commentary">
        <p n="B14">The word <foreign>striyau</foreign> appears like <foreign>sriyau</foreign>.</p>
        <p n="C6">The word <foreign>devapūjāṅ<unclear>ś</unclear>śā</foreign>can also be read <foreign>devapūjāṅgā</foreign>.</p>
        <p n="C20">Regarding <foreign>pratyekan tu dvi-ku<choice>
              <orig>d</orig>
              <corr>ḍ</corr>
            </choice>avau</foreign>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00368.xml">K. 368</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00386.xml">K. 386</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00435.xml">K. 435</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK01115.xml">K. 1115</ref> and <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK01170.xml">K. 1170</ref> has <foreign>pratyekam ekaśaḥ prasthau</foreign>.</p>
        <p n="C21">Regarding <foreign>Ekamuṣṭis tvacaḥ pathyā</foreign>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00368.xml">K. 368</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00386.xml">K. 386</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00435.xml">K. 435</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK01115.xml">K. 1115</ref> and <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK01170.xml">K. 1170</ref> has <foreign>tvaksārddhamuṣṭiḥ pathyās tu</foreign>.</p>
        <p n="C22">Regarding <foreign>dārvyā Ekāc<unclear>ch</unclear>idākhyātā</foreign>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00368.xml">K. 368</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00386.xml">K. 386</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK00435.xml">K. 435</ref>, <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK01115.xml">K. 1115</ref> and <ref target="DHARMA_INSCIK01170.xml">K. 1170</ref> has <foreign>dārvībhidādvayañ cātha</foreign>.</p>
        <p n="D15">There is no space between the <foreign>pāda</foreign>s a and b.</p>
        <p n="D17">There is no space between the <foreign>pāda</foreign>s a and b.</p>
        <p n="D18">There is no space between the <foreign>pāda</foreign>s c and d.</p>
